title: Life After Winning An Olympic Silver Medal | MyKayla Skinner
description: Back from winning silver in the Gymnastic Vault Finals at the Tokyo 2020 Olympics, gymnast MyKayla Skinner joins Reed Duchscher and Blake Robbins to chat about her journey to achieving her Olympic dreams, managing mental health as an Olympians, and plans now that the Games are over.
